reviews.review_text:
Spanish Lady comes to me.. Cryptical>Other1>Cryptical
Becoming some what of a rare occurrence.

You know people who complained about repeats in the 1980's would do well to check out the set lists on this 3 night Cali run.
I would put this behind the Second Night but better than the first. (Although a few of the rarities the opening night grab ones attention). To me this is the smoothest of the three shows almost like it took them until the final night to get to optimal overdrive.(That said I really like some of the funky nooks and crannies of the first two shows.)
Smokestack Lightning as Set two opener!
"Where you been all last night, you been out darling, and your pants don't fit you right" -Pigpen
A nice smooth Second Set with a big Good Lovin' closer
I noticed this from the notes section:
"project started 7-28-01, finished 10-15-01
thank you all for your kind patience"
Some music to get thru dark times..
